   $(document).ready(function () {
   	$('ul.expanddetails li:not(.sel) .details').hide();
 
   	// click on a section to expand it
   	$('ul.expanddetails a.sectiontitle').each(function () {
   		//search DOM only once and save results to data()
   		$(this).data('group', $(this).parents('.subcat').attr('rel'))
 		.data('details', $(this).parent().find('.details'))
 		.data('li', $(this).parent());
 
 
   		$(this).bind("click", function (e) {
   			//alert("GROUP IS "+$(this).data('group'));
   			var my = $(this);
 
   			if (my.data('li').hasClass('sel')) {
   				my.data('li').removeClass('sel');
   				my.data('details').slideUp('fast');
   			} else {
   				my.data('li').addClass('sel');
   				my.data('details').slideDown('fast');
   			}
   			return false;
   		});
   	});
 
 
   	$('.openall').each(function () {
   		//search DOM only once and save results to data()
   		$(this).data('group', $(this).parents('.subcat').attr('rel'));
   		$(this).bind("click", function (e) {
   			var my = $(this);
 
   			$('ul.expanddetails li:not(.sel)').each(function () {
 
   				if ($(this).find('.sectiontitle').data('group') == my.data('group')) {
   					$(this).addClass('sel').find('.details').show();
   				}
 
   			});
 
   		});
   	});
 
   	$('.closeall').each(function () {
   		//search DOM only once and save results to data()
   		$(this).data('group', $(this).parents('.subcat').attr('rel'));
   		$(this).bind("click", function (e) {
   			var my = $(this);
   			$('ul.expanddetails li.sel').each(function () {
 
   				if ($(this).find('.sectiontitle').data('group') == my.data('group')) {
   					$(this).removeClass('sel').find('.details').hide();
   				}
 
   			});
 
   		});
   	});
 
   });
   </script>
